strings:
<voice_0x01000C88><se_low>King Trode: Magnificent! What a dutiful maid,
worrying about her master so! I am impressed!
<voice_0x01000C89><se_low>King Trode: A faithful retainer like her is a most precious treasure to a king. And you say she's about the same age as my dear Medea?

<voice_0x01000C8A><se_low>King Trode: Very well! Now, this is an order!
I want you to help this maid with her request!
<voice_0x01000C8B><se_low>King Trode: I beg your pardon? A detour? Well, if you get onto it quickly, it won't be a problem, will it!?
<voice_0x01000C8C><se_low>King Trode: Off we go! We must lend a hand to this delightful maid of yours!
